  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q106",
  "body": "What do we pray for in the sixth petition?\n\nIn the sixth petition, which is, 'And lead us not into temptation, but deliver us from evil,' we pray, That God would either keep us from being tempted to sin, or support and deliver us when we are tempted.",
